Some gunmen have reportedly attacked the Government Technical Secondary School, Mararaban Kajuru in Kajuru Local Government Area of the state, abducting the principal of the school. This is coming barely a week after the abduction of six female pupils and two staff members of the Engravers College, Chikun Local Government Area of the State. The PPRO of the Kaduna State Police Command, DSP Yakubu Sabo who was called to confirm the incident is yet to respond to text messages and calls. details later To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .